Usage: reset_pulse_clock_max_width [-help] <object_list> [-transitive_fanout]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>          # List of objects: pulse generator cells, pulse
                       # generator library cells, clocks or current_design
                       # (string, required)
-transitive_fanout     # Pulse width value for transitive fanout
                       # (bool, optional)